    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to people or corporate bodies who own or run manufacturing plants for making clothing, which is covering for the torso, limbs, hands, feet, and head for warmth, fashion, or to cover nudity. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
